items.author: Fannovel16
items.title: ControlNet Preprocessors
items.description: This extension provides preprocessor nodes for using controlnet.

items.author: comfyanonymous
items.title: ComfyUI_experiments/sampler_tonemap
items.description: Increasing the CFG prevents the degradation of color accuracy.

items.author: Dr.Lt.Data
items.title: ComfyUI Impact Pack
items.description: To implement the feature of automatically detecting faces and enhancing details, various detection nodes and detailers provided by the Impact Pack can be applied.

items.author: biegert
items.title: CLIPSeg
items.description: This extension provides a feature that generates segment masks on an image using a text prompt. When used in conjunction with Impact Pack, it enables applications such as DDSD.

items.author: BadCafeCode
items.title: Masquerade Nodes
items.description: This extension provides a way to recognize and enhance masks for faces similar to Impact Pack.

items.author: BlenderNeko
items.title: ComfyUI Cutoff
items.description: By using this extension, prompts like 'blue hair' can be prevented from interfering with other prompts by blocking the attribute 'blue' from being used in prompts other than 'hair'.

items.author: BlenderNeko
items.title: Advanced CLIP Text Encode
items.description: There are differences in the processing methods of prompts, such as weighting and scheduling, between A1111 and ComfyUI. With this extension, various settings can be used to implement prompt processing methods similar to A1111. As this feature is also integrated into ComfyUI Cutoff, please download the Cutoff extension if you plan to use it in conjunction with Cutoff.

items.author: BlenderNeko
items.title: ComfyUI Noise
items.description: The extension provides an unsampler that reverses the sampling process, allowing for a function similar to img2img alt to be implemented.

items.author: lilly1987
items.title: simple wildcard for ComfyUI
items.description: This extension provides features such as a wildcard function that randomly selects prompts belonging to a category and the ability to directly load lora from prompts.

items.author: Davemane42
items.title: Visual Area Conditioning / Latent composition
items.description: ComfyUI already provides the ability to composite latents by default. However, this extension makes it more convenient to use by visualizing the composite area.

items.author: LEv145
items.title: ImagesGrid
items.description: This tool provides a viewer node that allows for checking multiple outputs in a grid, similar to the X/Y Plot extension.

items.author: gamert
items.title: ComfyUI_tagger
items.description: This extension generates clip text by taking an image as input and using the Deepbooru model.

items.author: szhublox
items.title: Auto-MBW
items.description: This node takes two models, merges individual blocks together at various ratios, and automatically rates each merge, keeping the ratio with the highest score.

items.author: szhublox
items.title: Auto-MBW
items.description: This extension is a ComfyUI wrapper for 'tomesd' that improves generation speed through token merging.
